# Technical Audit Report - MindWell Platform

This report provides a detailed breakdown of the current implementation status of all features and technologies within the MindWell Mental Wellness & AI Therapy Platform.

## Summary Status
- ✅ **Fully Implemented**: Core features are functional and production-ready.
- ⚠️ **Partially Implemented**: Features exist but are either demo-only, incomplete, or missing integrations.
- ❌ **Not Implemented**: No code or configuration exists in the codebase.

---

## 🎨 Features
| Feature | Status | Details |
| :--- | :---: | :--- |
| AI Chatbot Therapist | ✅ | **Implemented** in [chatController.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/controllers/chatController.js). Uses Gemini 2.5 Flash API with custom therapist system prompts and crisis detection. Production-ready. |
| Video Consultation | ❌ | **Not Implemented**. No WebRTC or third-party video integration detected. |
| Mood Tracking Analytics | ✅ | **Implemented**. Backend [moodController.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/controllers/moodController.js) saves entries to MongoDB. Frontend [MoodPage.tsx](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/src/pages/Mood/MoodPage.tsx) visualizes real data with Recharts. Production-ready. |
| Subscription-based Plans | ⚠️ | **Partially Implemented**. Model [Subscription.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/models/Subscription.js) exists. Fixed-period (1 month) logic is in the controller. Missing recurring billing engine (Stripe). |
| Emergency Support | ⚠️ | **Partially Implemented**. [supportController.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/controllers/supportController.js) sends emails via Nodemailer. AI Chatbot detects crisis keywords but doesn't trigger automated alerts beyond logging. |
| Journal Management | ✅ | **Implemented** in [journalController.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/controllers/journalController.js). Supports full CRUD operations. Production-ready. |
| Community Forums | ✅ | **Implemented** in [communityController.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/controllers/communityController.js). Supports posts, comments, and categorization. Production-ready. |
| Appointment Booking | ✅ | **Implemented** in [appointmentController.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/controllers/appointmentController.js). Supports session scheduling and storage. Production-ready. |
| Payment Gateway | ⚠️ | **Partially Implemented**. Razorpay integration is functional. Missing Stripe. |

---

## 🛠️ Hard Technologies
| Technology | Status | Details |
| :--- | :---: | :--- |
| NLP Chatbot Integration | ✅ | **Fully Implemented** using Google's `@google/generative-ai` SDK. |
| Sentiment Analysis | ⚠️ | **Partially Implemented**. Basic intent detection logic in [chatController.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/controllers/chatController.js) for emotional classification. No advanced transformer-based sentiment piping yet. |
| Secure Medical Data | ⚠️ | **Partially Implemented**. Standard MongoDB storage. Missing field-level encryption or HIPAA/GDPR specific security headers for journals/mood. |

