## 🖥️ Backend
| Tech | Status | Details |
| :--- | :---: | :--- |
| Node.js + Express.js | ✅ | **Fully Implemented**. Primary server architecture. |
| REST APIs | ✅ | **Fully Implemented**. Modular routes and controllers for all core features. |
| GraphQL | ❌ | **Not Implemented**. All communication is via REST. |
| JWT Authentication | ✅ | **Fully Implemented** via [authMiddleware.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/middleware/authMiddleware.js). Secure token-based access control. |
| Redis / BullMQ | ❌ | **Not Implemented**. No caching layers or background queue systems present. |

