## 🔒 Security
| Feature | Status | Details |
| :--- | :---: | :--- |
| Role-Based Access | ✅ | **Implemented** in [authMiddleware.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/middleware/authMiddleware.js) ([requireRole](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/middleware/authMiddleware.js#9-17)). Supports user and admin roles. |
| API Rate Limiting | ✅ | **Implemented** via [securityMiddleware.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/middleware/securityMiddleware.js). |
| XSS / CSRF Protection | ⚠️ | **XSS Implemented** via `xss-clean`. CSRF protection is standard CORS/JWT based but no explicit CSRF tokens for form submits. |
| Helmet Security | ✅ | **Implemented**. Header security configured in [index.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/index.js). |
| Password Hashing | ✅ | **Implemented** in [User.js](file:///c:/Users/shiva/OneDrive/Desktop/mindwelll-main/server/models/User.js) using `bcryptjs`. |

